Introduction

Myah is a South Korean-American singer under TOP MEDIA.

In 2021, Myah was a contestant on MNET's survival show Girls Planet 999. She was eliminated in the final episode after ranking 11th overall and thus, being unable to debut with Kep1er.

On September 18, 2024, Myah was announced as the first member of the upcoming girl group ODD YOUTH. She debuted with them on November 1, 2024, with the release of their first single "Best Friendz".
